She smiled at Zeni. "It's ok, He's not going to hurt you. And we're 
not going to hurt him." She smiled and palyfully licked Zeni's nose.  
Then she walked over to Scat. "Hey, can I, can I shake paws with 
you?" she very slowly lifted her paw for Scat to shake.
